quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  43,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  43,1,Haa-Meeem
  43,2,Wal Kitaabil Mubeen
  43,3,Innaa ja'alnaahu Quraanan 'Arabiyyal la'allakum ta'qiloon
  43,4,Wa innahoo feee Ummil Kitaabi Ladainaa la'aliyyun hakeem
  43,5,Afanadribu 'ankumuz Zikra safhan an kuntum qawmam musrifeen
  43,6,Wa kam arsalnaa min Nabiyyin fil awwaleen
  43,7,Wa maa yaateehim min Nabiyyin illaa kaanoo bihee yasahzi'oon
  43,8,Fa ahlaknaaa ashadda minhum batshanw wa madaa masalul lawwaleen
  43,9,Wa la'in sa altahum man khalaqas samaawaati wal arda la yaqoolunna khalaqa hunnal 'Azeezul 'Aleem
  43,10,Allazee ja'ala lakumul arda mahdanw wa ja'ala lakum feehaa subulal la'allakum tahtadoon
  43,11,Wallazee nazzala minas samaaa'i maaa'am biqadarin fa anshamaa bihee baldatam maitaa' kazaalika tukhrajoon
  43,12,Wallazee khalaqal azwaaja kullahaa wa ja'ala lakum minal fulki wal-an'aami maa tarkaboon
  43,13,Litastawoo 'alaa zuhoorihee summa tazkuroo ni'mata Rabbikum izastawaitum 'alaihi wa taqooloo Subhaanal lazee sakhkhara lana haaza wa maa kunnaa lahoo muqrineen
  43,14,Wa innaaa ilaa Rabbinaa lamunqaliboon
  43,15,Wa ja'aloo lahoo min 'ibaadihee juz'aa; innal insaana lakafoorum mubeen�(section 1)
  43,16,Amit takhaza mimmaa yakhluqu banaatinw wa asfaakum bilbaneen
  43,17,Wa izaa bushshira ahaduhum bimaa daraba lir Rahmaani masalan zalla wajhuhoo muswaddanw wa hua kazeem
  43,18,Awa mai yunashsha'u fil hilyati wa huwa fil khisaami ghairu mubeen
  43,19,Wa ja'alul malaaa'ikatal lazeena hum 'ibaadur Rahmaani inaasaa; a shahidoo khalaqhum; satuktabu shahaa datuhum wa yus'aloon
  43,20,Wa qaaloo law shaaa'ar Rahmaanu maa 'abadnaahum; maa lahum bizaalika min 'ilmin in hum illaa yakhrusoon
  43,21,Am aatainaahum Kitaabam min qablihee fahum bihee mustamsikoon
  43,22,Bal qaalooo innaa wajadnaaa aabaaa'anaa 'alaaa ummatinw wa innaa 'alaaa aasaarihim muhtadoon
  43,23,Wa kazaalika maaa arsalnaa min qablika fee qaryatim min nazeerin illaa qaala mutrafoohaaa innaa wajadnaaa aabaaa'anaa 'alaaa ummatinw wa innaa 'alaaa aasaarihim muqtadoon
  43,24,Qaala awa law ji'tukum bi ahdaa mimmaa wajattum 'alaihi aabaaa'akum qaalooo innaa bimaaa ursiltum bihee kaafiroon
  43,25,Fantaqamnaa minhum fanzur kaifa kaana 'aaqibatul mukazzibeen�(section 2)
  43,26,Wa iz qaala Ibraaheemu liabeehi wa qawmiheee innane baraaa'um mimmaa ta'budo
  43,27,Illal lazee fataranee innahoo sa yahdeen
  43,28,Wa ja'alahaa Kalimatam baaqiyatan fee 'aqibihee la'al lahum yarji'oon
  43,29,Bal matta'tu haaa'ulaaa'i wa aabaaa'ahum hattaa jaaa'a humul haqqu wa Rasoolum mubeen
  43,30,Wa lammaa jaaa'ahumul haqqu qaaloo haazaa sihrunw wa innaa bihee kaafiroon
  43,31,Wa qaaloo law laa nuzzila haazal Quraanu 'alaa rajulim minal qaryataini 'azeem
  43,32,Ahum yaqsimoona rahmata Rabbik; Nahnu qasamnaa bainahum ma'eeshatahum fil hayaatid dunyaa wa rafa'naa ba'dahum fawqa ba'din darajaatil liyattakhiza ba'duhum ba'dan sukhriyyaa; wa rahmatu Rabbika khairum mimmaa yajma'oon
  43,33,Wa law laaa any yakoonan naasu ummatanw waahidatal laja'alnaa limany yakfuru bir Rahmaani libu yootihim suqufam min fiddatinw wa ma'aarija 'alaihaa yazharoon
  43,34,Wa libu yootihim abwaabanw wa sururan 'alaihaa yattaki'oon
  43,35,Wa zukhrufaa; wa in kullu zaalika lammaa mataa'ul hayaatid dunyaa; wal aakhiratu 'inda Rabbika lilmuttaqeen�(section 3)
  43,36,Wa mai ya'shu 'an zikrir Rahmaani nuqaiyid lahoo Shaitaanan fahuwa lahoo qareen
  43,37,Wa innahum la yasuddoo nahum 'anis sabeeli wa yahsaboona annahum muhtadoon
  43,38,Hattaaa izaa jaaa'anaa qaala yaa laita bainee wa bainaka bu'dal mashriqaini fabi'sal qareen
  43,39,Wa lai yanfa'akumul Yawma iz zalamtum annakum fil 'azaabi mushtarikoon
  43,40,Afa anta tusmi'us summa aw tahdil 'umya wa man kaana fee dalaalim mubeen
  43,41,Fa immaa nazhabanna bika fa innaa minhum muntaqimoon
  43,42,Aw nuriyannakal lazee wa'adnaahum fa innaa 'alaihim muqtadiroon
  43,43,Fastamsik billazeee oohi ya ilaika innaka 'alaa Siraatim Mustaqeem
  43,44,Wa innahoo lazikrul laka wa liqawmika wa sawfa tus'aloon
  43,45,Was'al man arsalnaa min qablika mir Rusulinaaa aja'alnaa min doonir Rahmaani aalihatany yu badoon�(section 4)
  43,46,Wa laqad arsalnaa Moosaa bi aayaatinaaa ilaa Fir'awna wa mala'ihee faqaala innee Rasoolu Rabbil 'aalameen
  43,47,Falammma jaaa'ahum bi aayaatinaaa izaa hum minhaa yadhakoon
  43,48,Wa maa nureehim min aayatin illaa hiya akbaru min ukhtihaa wa akhaznaahum bil'azaabi la'allahum yarji'oon
  43,49,Wa qaaloo yaaa ayyuhas saahirud'u lanaa Rabbaka bimaa 'ahida 'indaka innanaa lamuhtadoon
  43,50,Falammaa kashafnaa 'anhumul 'azaaba izaa hum yankusoon
  43,51,Wa naadaa Fir'awnu fee qawmihee qaala yaa qawmi alaisa lee mulku Misra wa haazihil anhaaru tajree min tahtee afalaa tubsiroon
  43,52,Am ana khairum min haazal lazee huwa maheenunw wa laa yuakaadu yubeen
  43,53,Falaw laa ulqiya 'alaihi aswiratum min zahabin awjaaa'a ma'ahul malaaa'ikatu muqtarineen
  43,54,Fastakhaffa qawmahoo fa ataa'ooh; innahum kaanoo qawman faasiqeen
  43,55,Falammaaa aasafoonan taqamnaa minhum fa aghraqnaahum ajma'een
  43,56,Faja'alnaahum salafanw wa masalal lil aakhireen�(section 5)
  43,57,Wa lammaa duribab nu Maryama masalan izaa qawmu ka minhu yasidoon
  43,58,Wa qaalooo 'a-aalihatunaa khairun am hoo; maa daraboohu laka illaa jadalaa; balhum qawmun khasimoon
  43,59,In huwa illaa 'abdun an'amnaa 'alaihi wa ja'alnaahu masalal li Baneee Israaa'eel
  43,60,Wa law nashaaa'u laja'alnaa minkum malaaa'ikatan fil ardi yakhlufoon
  43,61,Wa innahoo la'ilmul lis Saa'ati fala tamtarunna bihaa wattabi'oon; haazaa Siraatum Mustaqeem
  43,62,Wa laa yasuddan nakumush Shaitaanu innahoo lakum 'aduwwum mubeen
  43,63,Wa lammaa jaaa'a 'Eesaa bilbaiyinaati qaala qad ji'tukum bil Hikmati wa li-ubaiyina lakum ba'dal lazee takhtalifoona feehi fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  43,64,Innal laaha Huwa Rabbee wa Rabbukum fa'budooh; haaza Siraatum Mustaqeem
  43,65,Fakhtalafal ahzaabu mim bainihim fawailul lillazeena zalamoo min 'azaabi Yawmin aleem
  43,66,Hal yanzuroona illas Saa'ata an taatiyahum baghtatanw wa hum laa yash'uroon
  43,67,Al akhillaaa'u Yawma'izim ba'duhum liba'din 'aduwwun illal muttaqeen�(section 6)
  43,68,Yaa 'ibaadi laa khawfun 'alaikumul Yawma wa laaa antum tahzanoon
  43,69,Allazeena aamanoo bi Aayaatinaa wa kaanoo muslimeen
  43,70,Udkhulul Jannata antum wa azwaajukum tuhbaroon
  43,71,"Yutaafu 'alaihim bishaa fim min zahabinw wa akwaab, wa feehaa maatashtaheehil anfusu wa talazzul a'yunu wa antum feehaa khaalidoon"
  43,72,Wa tilkal jannatul lateee ooristumoohaa bimaa kuntum ta'maloon
  43,73,Lakum feehaa faakihatun kaseeratum minhaa taakuloon
  43,74,Innal mujrimeena fee 'azaabi jahannama khaalidoon
  43,75,Laa yufattaru 'anhum wa hum feehi mublisoon
  43,76,Wa maa zalamnaahum wa laakin kaanoo humuz zaalimeen
  43,77,Wa naadaw yaa Maaliku liyaqdi 'alainaa Rabbuka qaala innakum maakisson
  43,78,Laqad ji'naakum bilhaqqi wa laakinna aksarakum lilhaqqi kaarihoon
  43,79,Am abramooo amran fainnaa mubrimoon
  43,80,Am yahsaboona annaa laa nasma'u sirrahum wa najwaahum; balaa wa Rusulunaa ladaihim yaktuboon
  43,81,Qul in kaana lir Rahmaani walad; fa-ana awwalul 'aabideen
  43,82,Subhaana Rabbis samaawaati wal ardi Rabbil Arshi 'ammaa yasifoon
  43,83,Fazarhum yakhoodoo wa yal'aboo hattaa yulaaqoo Yawmahumul lazee yoo'adoon
  43,84,Wa Huwal lazee fissamaaa'i Ilaahunw wa fil ardi Ilaah; wa Huwal Hakeemul'Aleem
  43,85,Wa tabaarakal lazee lahoo mulkus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa wa 'indahoo 'ilmus Saa'ati wa ilaihi turja'oon
  43,86,Wa laa yamlikul lazeena yad'oona min doonihish shafaa'ata illaa man shahida bilhaqqi wa hum ya'lamoon
  43,87,Wa la'in sa altahum man khalaqahum la yaqoolun nallaahu fa annaa yu'fakoon
  43,88,Wa qeelihee yaa Rabbi inna haa'ulaaa'i qawmul laa yu'minoon
  43,89,Fasfah 'anhum wa qul salaam; fasawfa ya'lamoon�(section 7)
